<TITLE>
Yakwawiak, the Big Rump Bear (Yakwahe, Tagesho)
</TITLE>

<META NAME="description" CONTENT="Information and legends about the Native American monster Yakwawiak (or Tagesho),
a mythological beast from Algonquian folklore resembling a giant hairless bear or elephant.">
